' ============================================================
' 03 Feature 生命周期 DAG — 8 阶段
' ============================================================
@startuml docs/plantuml/03-feature-lifecycle
!theme plain

skinparam rectangle {
  FontSize 11
}

title Feature Lifecycle DAG — 8 Stages

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #333333
  FontSize 11
  ArrowColor #333333
}

title Feature Lifecycle DAG — 8 Stages

state A as "analyze-current-state" #lightblue
state G as "gap-analysis" #lightyellow
state SD as "solution-design" #lightyellow
state TB as "task-breakdown" #lightgreen
state I as "implementation" #lightgreen
state V as "local-validation" #lightgreen
state R as "architecture-review" #plum
state C as "acceptance" #plum

A --> G
G --> SD
SD --> TB
TB --> I
I --> V
V --> R
R --> C

note right of A : outputs: 01-current-state.md
note right of G : outputs: 02-gap-analysis.md
note right of SD : outputs: 03/04-*.md
note right of TB : outputs: 05-task-breakdown.md
note right of I : outputs: code changes
note right of V : outputs: validation/test-report.md
note right of R : outputs: architecture-review.md
note right of C : outputs: acceptance + release-notes.md

caption Stage confirmation required: solution-design | implementation | acceptance

@enduml